Package: eksiR
Title: Scrape Data from eksisozluk.com
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: person("Sefa", "Ozalp", email = "ozalpas [at] cardiff.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A webscraper for eksisozluk.com (sour dictionary) which is
    one of the top 20 sites in Turkey (https://www.alexa.com/topsites/countries/TR).
    It allows you to scrape data by entry number or topic URL and returns a neat tibble.
    The former method returns informative errors for deleted/removed entries. eksiR also allows for
    correct parsing data/time values scraped from eksisozluk.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.4)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    dplyr,
    rvest, 
    tibble,
    xml2,
    glue,
    purrr,
    xml2
Suggests: covr,
    testthat,
